sections.text:
22-5303. DEFINITIONS. As used in this chapter, unless the context requires otherwise:

(1) "Board" means the Idaho wolf depredation control board;

(2) "Brand board" means the state brand board;

(3) "Director" means either the director of the department of agriculture or the director of the department of fish and game, as so designated;

(4) "Wolf" means the Canis lupus species.

[22-5303, added 2014, ch. 188, sec. 2, p. 501.]
